<!--
  LunaGlass pin glyph — teardrop outer with inscribed hex centre.
  Reverted from the angular hex-head + shaft + V-point shape because
  the user reads that as an "arrow" while the teardrop reads as a
  proper map "pin." White strokes so consumers' tint colour wins.
-->
